5. Automation Scenarios - What to Test
Below are typical scenarios you should automate for any API. The "Bookstore API" is used as an example.
Verify HTTP status codes - e.g., 200, 201, 400, 404.
Validate response body content - message, property existence, data types.
Check JSON schema - structure matches the contract.
Use environment/collection variables - to switch endpoints (dev/staging/prod).
