Comprehensive Notes: Web Services & API Testing - Draft

Course Overview

Instructor-led training on web service and API testing

Tool used: SoapUI (open-source version covers almost all features)

No prior knowledge required - starts from absolute beginner level

Covers both manual and automated testing for SOAP and REST services

