Complete Guide to API Test Automation Using SoapUI - From SDET Perspective - -draft
This document is a standalone resource for automation testers and SDETs with 2–5 years of experience. It covers API testing with SoapUI, focusing on end‑to‑end workflows, assertions, property transfer, Groovy script assertions, and integration with CI/CD. All explanations are original and structured for both practical project work and interview readiness.

