7. Expanding to Update Place (PUT)
Although the transcript only shows Add, Get, and Delete, a real end‑to‑end test should include Update.
7.1 Update Place Request
HTTP method: PUT

Path: /maps/api/place/update/json

Query parameter: key=qaclick123

Request body:

json
{
  "place_id": "${#TestCase#place_id}",
  "address": "70 winter walk, USA",
  "key": "qaclick123"
