8. Best Practices & Common Mistakes (From Real‑World Experience)

✅ Best Practices

Always use property transfers in SoapUI for dynamic data - never hardcode.

Parameterise endpoints and test data using test suite properties.

Keep the SoapUI project XML file under version control (Git).

Separate source code (src), libraries (lib), and compiled classes (bin).

